  Ra-228/Noch-T-bone-V    Blood                 $(0.18 / 365.25)
  Ra-228/T-marrow         T-marrow                  ---     # only for progeny of Thorium chain
  Ra-228/Liver1           Liver1                    ---
  Ra-228/Liver2           Liver2                    ---
  Ra-228/Spleen           Spleen                    ---     # only for progeny of Thorium chain
  Ra-228/Kidneys1         Kidneys1                  ---
  Ra-228/Kidneys2         Kidneys2                  ---
